# Environment setup
#
# Local:      copy .env.local.example → .env.local  (or use the pre-filled .env.local)
# Production: use .env.production → import into Vercel env settings
#
# Required variables:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
#   DATABASE_URL
#   DIRECT_URL
